Class TravelTimesForTrip

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.transitime.db.structs.TravelTimesForTrip

    @Entity
public class TravelTimesForTrip
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Keeps track of travel times for a trip. Can be shared amongst trips if the travel times are similar. But need separate travel times for every trip pattern.
